snippet.title: Space Slurpies Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
How long can you survive in the colorful galaxy of Space Slurpies? In this multiplayer arcade game, control luminescent snakes that grow in length and size. Collect as much food as possible and survive each round without colliding with yourself and other players in fast-pacing battles.

Wishlist here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1334910/Space_Slurpies/
Download song here: https://open.spotify.com/track/2K1dLeA4rmFCY6e8DGaovu
Talk to us here: https://discord.gg/eFqWcT5
